# =============================================================================
# HACKT RUNTIME – MASTER GITIGNORE
# Architecture: React (Vite) + Rust (Tauri) + Python (FastAPI)
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. SENSITIVE DATA & SECRETS (CRITICAL)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Never commit API keys, tokens, or local environment configs
.env
.env.local
.env.production
*.pem
*.key
*.cert
src-tauri/.env
backend_service/.env
supabase.json
config secrets.json

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 2. AI MODELS & KNOWLEDGE VAULT (LARGE BINARY FILES)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Models are 4-10GB. Do not commit. Download via script or use Git LFS.
models/*.gguf
models/*.bin
models/*.onnx
models/*.pt
models/*.pth
models/indices/
models/vault.lance/
models/vault.graph/
models/bm25_index.pkl
models/file_summaries.json
data/
*.lance
*.graph

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 3. FRONTEND (React + Vite + TypeScript)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
node_modules/
dist/
build/
.vite/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
package-lock.json
yarn.lock
pnpm-lock.yaml

